trans-unit.target: TEXT_VOICEMAN_03401_000050_KRILE<tab>I leave the Goddess in your capable hands. Just watch out for her worshipers...
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03401_000010_CID<tab>All right! Time to deactivate the barrier!
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03401_000030_CID<tab>Godssake! I didn't count on the bloody thing moving!
TEXT_VOICEMAN_03401_000040_CID<tab>The smoke is too thick! Can't see a damn thing! You'll have to press on alone!
